Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 親愛的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的信用卡賬單\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just going through your credit card bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 來了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Uh, ye... Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里沒別的人 Molly\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Nobody else is home, Molly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐下\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直像你的月事\N{\fs38}{\fs38}This is becoming, like, an every month thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們就一個經濟來源\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, now that we're a one-income family
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的得節省點了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}we really have got to watch our spending.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近一直很節約啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, I've been really good lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去星巴克了 不做指甲了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}no Starbucks, no manicures,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 只去看了一次手相  - 什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I've only had one palm reading. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 Olga夫人說了你會生氣的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}See? Madam Olga said you'd be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真好笑\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛把這些賬單過了一遍\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, I was going over these bills,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為有些地方的錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and I think there's a few more areas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全可以省下來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}where we can cut back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 說來聽聽  - 比如這個\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Let's hear it. - Well, how about this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"上蠟 脫蠟"處 是洗車嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}"Wax On, Wax Off" Place, is that a car wash?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這完全可以在自家車道上搞定\N{\fs38}{\fs38}'Cause I could do that in the driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的比基尼蜜蠟 你想在車道上搞定嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's my bikini wax, you want to do that in the driveway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把這個歸到"醫療開支"里\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We'll file that under "Medical expenses"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們不需要的 NFL付費運動節目包\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Here's what we don't need... NFL Sports Package.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我們都有好處的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We both need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不在這看橄欖球\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If I'm not watching football here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會去酒吧里看\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我進了酒吧 就會喝啤酒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If I'm at a bar, having a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在比賽是在周日 周一和周四\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Now, games are Sunday, Monday, and Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每場比賽至少三瓶酒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Let's say at least three beers per game,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上十七個禮拜 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}times 17 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上季后賽\N{\fs38}{\fs38}plus playoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了省50塊錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Saving $50 has cost you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換來一個酗酒的丈夫\N{\fs38}{\fs38}one husband to alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都比這好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Anything's better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么  - 什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- What? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就有一個\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, here, here's a perfect example
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要的奢侈品\N{\fs38}{\fs38}of a luxury item we do not need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶裝水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Bottled water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 不喝水會死的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike, we need water to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這\N{\fs38}{\fs38}right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 還是免費的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, and it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從密歇根湖直接運過來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}From Lake Michigan to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是絕世好水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}See? Perfectly good water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要喝還是要用來漆房子啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You gonna drink that or paint the house with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 讓這里面的礦物質\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, give it a second, you just got to let the minerals
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和維他命沉淀一下\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and vitamins sink to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 我還有個主意 你喝那個\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Or... I have another idea... how about you drink that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝罐裝水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'll drink the bottled water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人喝能喝更久\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It'll last twice as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看誰給我們省了一半的水錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Who just cut our water bill in half?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒水了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Out of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有的是呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mine's still full.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也馬上就有了 讓我換桶水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mine will be... let me just swap out this dead soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你舉不起那桶水的 我來幫你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You can't lift that jug, let me help you with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的 這是我的水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, I got it, it's my water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能換的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I can change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就享受肝炎陰影的籠罩吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just enjoy your "Cloudy with a Chance of Hep C"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要幫忙嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Would you like some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能搞定\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\fs38}{\fs38}God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Easy-peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 現在就需要\N{\fs38}{\fs38}All right, so it's just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它翻一面了 開始\N{\fs38}{\fs38}a full flip, and there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝極了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把整壺都留下吧 我昨晚幾乎沒睡\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just leave the pot. I hardly slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該弄個人形抱枕\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, you should get a body pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我有了之后 每天都睡得像嬰兒一樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ever since I got one, I've been sleeping like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的醒來后發現大拇指在嘴巴里\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I literally woke up with my thumb in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴我你另一個拇指在哪\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, don't tell me where the other thumb was,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚的噩夢夠多了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I had enough nightmares last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過那個\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Have you heard the one where you wake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被室友搞人形抱枕時發出的激情聲音\N{\fs38}{\fs38}to the passionate sounds of your roommate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒的噩夢嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}humping a body pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 我只是把抱枕翻到涼的那一面而已\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I told you, I was just flipping it to the cool side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大腿太熱了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}My thighs get hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在夢里首先我所有牙齒都碎了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, this dream started with all my teeth crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這通常表示著無能為力\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, that usually represents a feeling of powerlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如你的生活開始分崩離析\N{\fs38}{\fs38}like your life is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者也可以反映你的口腔衛生情況\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Or it could reflect your dental hygiene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用停車罰單剔牙\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Picking your teeth with a parking citation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和用牙線是不一樣的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}is not the same as flossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牙掉光之后 我一下子到了廁所\N{\fs38}{\fs38}After my teeth fell out, I was suddenly in a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在馬桶上 錢就開始從那里涌出來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I sat on a pot, and money just started pouring out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬幣啦 鈔票啦 什么都有\N{\fs38}{\fs38}coins, bills, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要去撿的時候 它們就全被沖掉了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}But when I tried to grab it, it all flushed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉錢出來\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Diarrhea money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種夢很常見\N{\fs38}{\fs38}This is a very common dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹瀉表示你對生活缺乏控制\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Your loose bowels represent a lack of control in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢可以代表任何東西\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The money could be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Like money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah! Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照我和Molly還款的速度\N{\fs38}{\fs38}At the rate me and Molly are paying down our debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的第一個家很可能就是養老院了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}our first home's gonna be a nursing home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Boo-hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信用等級糟透了 我根本就不能欠債\N{\fs38}{\fs38}My credit rating is so bad, I can't even get into debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mm!
