Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是告訴你一聲\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就去找工作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm going out and getting a job today,
