Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找工作 我有個哥們開了個學校\N{\fs38}{\fs38}looking for a job, I got a buddy who owns a school
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門教外國人開車\N{\fs38}{\fs38}teaching foreigners how to drive cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不知道這有多掙錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You'd be surprised how much money you can make
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非法移民市場可大了去了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}exploiting the undocumented immigrant market.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹是個碩士 Vince\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I have a master's degree, Vince, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我不至于去干那個吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I think I can get something a little bit better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的性福說拜拜吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You may never get laid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么技能嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}So, do you have any skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 我曾是有編制的芝加哥教師\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Uh, yeah, I was a teacher for the Chicago school system
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去十年里一直是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}for the last ten years, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是沒有技能了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh. No skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 我有技能呢 我能打字\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, no, no, I have, I have skills... I can type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能熟練使用電腦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm very good with computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯呀\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, that's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得粉刷匠怎么樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Uh, how do you feel about house painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉刷匠\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我不可能一開始就讓你做粉刷工作\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, I couldn't start you off as a painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許先刮大白 或當小工\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, maybe a scraper or a prepper.
