Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是個碩士\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I-I have a master's degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的專業是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, if it's a master's degree in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空調維修 那我們正需要這種人才\N{\fs38}{\fs38}air-conditioning repair, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我的專業是中世紀文學\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Uh, no, it's in medieval literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我只是覺得\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Um, I just, I just think that I have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了體力活 我還可以做些別的工作回饋社會\N{\fs38}{\fs38}a little more to offer the world than manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的社會才懶得管你呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, the world doesn't give a hot crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想聽我說句大實話\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do you mind if, uh, we get real for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比剛才那句還實在嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Realer than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都完了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We're all screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你現在沒錢 你永遠也富不了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If you don't have money now, you are never getting any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有錢的那仨\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Because the three guys that have it all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會把錢白分給你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}are not sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找工作的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Are you sure that you're the one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是問錯負責人了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm supposed to be talking to about getting a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒沒工作 實話告訴你吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}There are no jobs. In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家中介公司兩周內就要倒了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}this agency is shutting down in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們全都要失業了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We're all getting laid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛買了一輛裝備齊全的福特福克斯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And I just got a fully-loaded Ford Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯嘛\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Those are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能當房子住嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Nice enough to live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說起來 我 我該\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know what, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該走了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm probably just gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個給你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, you know... how about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的時候加個菜吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}get yourself a little treat at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請客\N{\fs38}{\fs38}on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天保佑你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我只會去拿這去買酒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know I'm gonna spend this on liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到我淪落至此\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Can't believe this is the only job I could get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個碩士\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I have a master's degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學車就是為了當出租車司機\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm just doing this so I can get a job driving a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是個博士呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And I have a PhD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害啊你 不會開車的博士\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, good for you, Dr. Don't Have a Driver's License.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十和二\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ten and two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是十一和一 十和二\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's 11 and one! Ten and two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 這是我和Molly第一次吵得這么兇\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know, this is me and Molly's first big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩口子哪有不拌嘴的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, that's what happens with couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得我倆第一次吵架\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I remember our first big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶口琴來上班那次嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The day you brought harmonica to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再之前那次\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No. Before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從你手里搶走了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}When I snatched that second double cheeseburger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個雙層芝士漢堡\N{\fs38}{\fs38}out of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是啊 那次太糟了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, right, that was a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你咬了我一口\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah. You bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現那不是漢堡的時候就松口了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I let up when I realized it wasn't hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不太了解\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I-I just didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時的情況\N{\fs38}{\fs38}the issues that you were going through,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怎么說 我也是因為愛你才那么做的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but you know, I did it out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我記得\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我就加入暴食者匿名互戒會了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It was right after that that I joined OA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Molly\N{\fs38}Molly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也在那\N{\fs38}{\fs38}She was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了我的人生\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Changed my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是Molly\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, Molly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Molly\N{\fs38}Molly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 開什么玩笑\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, you got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊 走啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Drive. Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅燈呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's a red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就 看看左右兩邊 開車 開車\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Then... check both ways, but go, go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開車\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這是要去哪呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明正看著我啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}She was looking right at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 還沒見過誰這樣氣沖沖地開走一輛普銳斯的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Wow. Never seen somebody storm off in a Prius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一點噪音都沒有 可有時無聲勝有聲\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Didn't make any noise, but it sure made her point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著她\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Follow that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 甩不掉那兩個傻瓜\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Damn it, we can't shake these clowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察在后面 不是應該靠邊停車嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Aren't we supposed to pull over for the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃爍燈和警笛都開了時才要\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Only if there's lights and a siren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Gah! Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天吶\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 專心開車 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just keep it together, professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向左轉\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and make a left up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別打燈\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Don't use your signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他們就知道我們往哪邊轉了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}they'll know which way we're turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉彎時加速就好了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Just accelerate through the turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學著點\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不懂那女人為什么還來學車\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't know why that woman's taking classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她剛怎么轉彎的沒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You see the way she just took that corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Molly 靠邊停車 我們得談談\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Molly, pull over, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察居然認識你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}The police know you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是罪犯吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Are you a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在我是你的救星\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, I'm your one chance out of this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減速帶\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Speed bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減速帶\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Speed bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想八卦的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know, I hate to pry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可很明顯 這都是因為\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but obviously, this is a result
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的伴侶\N{\fs38}{\fs38}of a lack of communication
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺乏溝通才這樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}between you and your spouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 閉嘴\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Shut up, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想說 你可以做好的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm just saying, I know how you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 這不是我的錯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hey, I'm not in the wrong, here.
