Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你都在干嘛 不但沒去想解決方法\N{\fs38}{\fs38}See what you did, there? Instead of trying to find a solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在怪她\N{\fs38}{\fs38}you're trying to lay blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒搞錯吧 就算是她做錯了 我也不對\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Really? So even when she's wrong I don't get to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧普拉說過 "婚姻或真理"\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Like Oprah says, "Do you want to be right
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你選哪個"\N{\fs38}{\fs38}or do you want to be married?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧普拉就沒結婚啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oprah isn't married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 但她有Gayle\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, she's got Gayle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}奧普拉好友 有傳兩人為同性戀伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 Molly 快停車\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Come on, Molly, pull over the car, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 讓我停車吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Please, please let me pull over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你非要這么遵守法律的話\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, fine. If you're gonna be such a stickler for the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠也別指望能在這當上出租車司機了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}you're never gonna make it as a cabbie in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她是我老婆\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I know she's my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這還是逃避追捕吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but this is still evading arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三思而后行\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Don't go in with a hot head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住 要聆聽 應答\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Remember, listen, acknowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受 道歉\N{\fs38}{\fs38}admit, and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Laaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧普拉說的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oprah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干嘛啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在賺自己的錢啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I am trying to earn my own money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這太可笑了  - 為什么\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- This is ridiculous. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得很對 你賺的錢又不是我的錢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}What you said is true... the money you make is not my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是你的錢  - 不 才不是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- It is your money. - No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整天游手好閑 揮金如土\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm not working, I'm just spending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一天忙到晚 努力想成為一名作家\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, you're working at trying to be a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道我能不能行\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't even know if I'm good enough to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你可以的  - 你又怎么知道 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}- You are. - How do you know? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都不知道 所以每天想這想那\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I...I don't even know. And that's what scares the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就感到害怕不安 然后我就\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Then I get scared, and I get nervous, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去逛街 一去逛街\N{\fs38}{\fs38}go shopping, and if I go shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會買那些蠢鞋 就為了讓自己好受點\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I buy stupid shoes, all trying to make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你好受點了嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do they make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你應該留著\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Then you should keep 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 可以的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你開心\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I want you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果你不開心\N{\fs38}{\fs38}'Cause when you're not happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也痛苦不堪\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話\N{\fs38}{\fs38}In that case, there's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再有個包和腰帶 我會更開心的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}there's a purse and a belt that might put me over the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 別得寸進尺  - 知道了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Don't push it. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的對 我打算\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're right. And I'm going to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要更加努力工作 變得更好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm going to work really hard to be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把我的信用卡給你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm gonna give you my credit cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不用這樣  - 我就要這樣 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}- You don't have to do that. - No, I want-I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經取消你的信用卡了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I already canceled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷開的你也取消了嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Even the ones you don't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是被你吃定了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're gonna be the death of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家見\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'll see you at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有麻煩了嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Are we in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 在下個紅綠燈處轉彎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, no. Just take a turn at the next light and head
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往密歇根大道走\N{\fs38}{\fs38}towards Michigan Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把新買的包和腰帶退回去\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I've got a purse and a belt I need to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想退掉這些東西 太搞笑了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, I'd like to return these. Uh, funny story...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到家后 發現我老公\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I got home, and my husband had already
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我買了一樣的鞋子 一樣的腰帶\N{\fs38}{\fs38}bought me the same shoes, the same belt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一樣的包\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and the same purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真是心有靈犀呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, does he know me or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鞋都被你穿過了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You wore these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, no, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是熱的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}They're still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那把包和腰帶退了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}All right, then take back the purse and belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的婚姻都命懸一線了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Come on, my frickin' marriage is on the line here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最多只能跟你換張折價券\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Best I can do is give you a store credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我還是都不退了吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, I'll take the purse and the belt.
